    ts:sourceFullText """# DGAV | Hiring of Senior Technician – Provision of Services (Covenant)

DGAV |

Hiring of Senior Technician – Provision of Services (Covenant)

The Directorate-General for Food and Veterinary Medicine (DGAV) informs that it is receiving expressions of interest for the hiring of Senior Technicians, on a service provision basis, in the form of an agreement, lasting until December 31, 2026.

Distribution and desired profile
Division Office of Animal Genetic Resources
3 Senior Technicians
to support the performance of official controls on the Control Plan for Animal Germinal Product Establishments – PCEPGA, Official Control Plan for studbooks and Breeding and Conservation Plans for Breeds – PCAC and Evaluation of payment requests under PEPAC support to the executing entities
Location
:

Lisbon and Porto
Qualifications
: Degree in the areas of Agrarian/Agricultural Sciences and Agriculture; Veterinary Science / Zootechnics.

Interested parties should send
Updated curriculum vitae
and other relevant elements for:
secdsga@dgav.pt
For more information, the DGAV institutional website can be consulted or clarification can be requested through the contact indicated.

May 22, 2026""" ;
