    ts:sourceFullText """# Simulation exercises focused on procedures in the event of avian influenza

Simulation exercises focused on procedures in the event of avian influenza

In order to provide you with the best possible service, we use cookies.

This consent to the use of cookies will allow us to process your browsing behavior on this website and to process unique identifiers.

Opting out or withdrawing consent may adversely affect some of the features or services provided on this website.

Technical cookies are strictly necessary for the functioning of this website and its services.

Without them, this site would not function properly.

For example, it would not be possible to follow the safety policies on the site.

Preference cookies allow us to remember your basic choices and improve your user experience.

For example, setting the language or allowing you to stay permanently logged in.

Analytical cookies are collected on our website by a script by Google Inc., which then anonymizes this data.

After anonymization, it is no longer personal data, because anonymized cookies cannot be assigned to a specific user or a specific person.

We only work with cookies in anonymized form.

Therefore, we cannot determine the behavior of a specific user from cookies.

Technical storage or access that is used solely for anonymous statistical purposes.

Without subpoena, voluntary compliance by your ISP, or other records from a third party, information stored or obtained for this purpose alone cannot normally be used to identify you.

We use marketing cookies for the purpose of using Google Maps and Youtube, as well as for sharing on Facebook and Twitter.""" ;
