    ts:sourceDocumentTitle "National strategy on health and safety at work, approved by the State-Regions Conference" ;
    ts:sourceFullText """# National strategy on health and safety at work, approved by the State-Regions Conference

National strategy on health and safety at work, approved by the State-Regions Conference

