egard-et-BassacCause-de-Clérans (northern part)Clermont-de-BeauregardFouleixLalinde (northern part)Liorac-sur-LouyreMauzac-et-Grand-Castang (northern part)Paunat (northern part)Paunat (norther

n p

art) north)PézulsPressignac-VicqSaint-Amand-de-VergtSaint-Avit-de-VialardSaint-Félix-de-VilladeixSaint-Foy-de-Longas (south of th

